fields.name: Square One
fields.description:
Square One boasts a brand new colorful and spacious interior perfect for that lunch with friends, business meetings, or a little you time.

We pride ourselves on using the freshest of ingredients in our food preparation and work for hand in hand with our artisan roaster to produce fantastic coffee to tingle your taste buds.

fields.name: China Sichuan
fields.description: Located at the heart of South Dublin, our elegant and stylish decor and most attentive staff will ensure every visit to China Sichuan Restaurant will be an experience to remember. While closed at present due to COVID, the restaurant opens for lunch and dinner and offers customers both an A La Carte Menu and a carefully designed Set Menu to give a perfectly balanced taste for all specialties.

fields.name: Woodfire and Green
fields.description:
At Woodfire & Green, our team of chefs have been designing, crafting and perfecting the unique flavours for our dishes using the finest and freshest of ingredients for over 20 years.

When we opened our doors in 2016, our family’s vision was a simple one: to make quality our top priority and provide our local community with a service that is warm, personal and friendly.

We are currently open for Lunch Tuesday - Friday 11am-3pm & Friday - Saturday 5pm-9pm for Dine in & Click & Collect Friday & Saturday 5pm-9pm

fields.name: Michie Sushi
fields.description: The word Michie in Japanese means “filled with smiles and laughter”. It makes us happy when a customer approaches us and says “thank you, that was delicious.” Michie Sushi is a family business; we take pride in our returning customers. We started Michie Sushi as a take away in Ranelagh in 2007. Soon, catering and deliveries were added. Due to demand, we opened a small restaurant in 2011. In our first year, we won McKenna’s Best Sushi in Ireland, an award we have won every year since. We have also won Best Casual Dining in the Restaurant Awards and Best Ethnic Restaurant by Georgina Campbell.

fields.name: La Dolce Vita
fields.description: Modern Family-Friendly Italian Restaurant with Authentic Italian Dishes and Pizza along with Wine, Cocktails, and Beer available on Draft and by the Bottle.

fields.name: Musasi
fields.description: Our style of sushi is called a gunkan-maki battle ship roll, since the tight nori wrap resembles battleships.

fields.name: Zambrero
fields.description:
Zambrero is healthy, Mexican inspired food that also helps stop world hunger. Every burrito or bowl purchased means a meal donated to someone in need with Plate 4 Plate. 

It's a win for your body, mind, soul and taste buds. 

We call it Feel Good Mex.

fields.name: Bashu Renjia
fields.description: M & L Chinese Restaurant Bashu Renjia was selected by McKenna as one of the 100 best restaurants in Ireland from 2014 to 2017. When moving here, you will taste real Chinese cuisine.
